# Network access

This project requires internet access for:

- MLB data ingestion (pybaseball, MLB Stats API, free public stats sources)
- `pip install` and package updates
- API and library documentation lookups

When a task needs external data or network commands, use network permissions proactively. Do not skip ingest, API calls, or installs because of sandbox concerns.

Document any new external data sources in DEV.md.
